		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="indent(8)">10</p>
			<p rend="indent(6)"><addressee>Reverend Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(7)"><placeName>371 Walnut St</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(8)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(9)"><placeName>P</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(5)">L.A.</p>
			<pb n="2R"/>
			<p rend="indent(8)"><placeName>Cincinnati</placeName> <date>18<hi rend="sup">th</hi> May 1847</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Mr Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Dr Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">I have been prevented addressing you<lb/> of late by a pressure of business however in the interim<lb/> I have learned nothing that would be of interest to you<lb/> I was handed the enclosed advertisement for insertion 3<lb/> times in the Occident please attend to it if not too late.<lb/>  I have yet on hand a small amt collected of subscribers<lb/> which I will forward to you by opportunity&#8212;I am<lb/> instructed by <persName>Mr I Goldberg </persName>and also by <persName>Mr Aub</persName><lb/> to discontinue their Occident&#44; <persName>Mr G</persName> does not now live<lb/> in <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName> and I saw him but  few weeks back<lb/> <persName>Mr A.</persName> was absent <placeName>East</placeName> when I collected his subscription<lb/> or he says he would have told me before&#8212;you will please<lb/> in future address my brothers numbers to <placeName>Louisville<lb/> Ky</placeName> his present residence.  You will please put the<lb/> following names on the subscription list of the Jewish<lb/> Publication Society&#8212;<persName>Alexander Mayer</persName> &#40;care <persName>Harris &#38;<lb/> Abraham</persName>&#41; <persName>Lawrence Bruel</persName> &#40;care <persName>Harris &#38; Abraham</persName>&#41;<lb/> <persName>Samuel Mayer</persName> &#40;care <persName>Arnold Springer &#38; Co</persName>&#41; <persName>Joseph Jonas</persName>&#44;<lb/> <persName>Daniel Wolf</persName>&#44; and <persName role="author">Lewis Abraham</persName> they are such<lb/> subscribers for the current year from its commencement<lb/> and wish all the numbers of this year&#44; I will send<lb/> on their subscriptions to you  With best wishes I<lb/> am Your friend</p>
				<p><persName role="author">Lewis Abraham</persName></p>
		</body>
	</text>
